data.value:
Ideal for solo travelers or individuals looking for a cozy space.
Offers all essential amenities for a comfortable stay, including a private bathroom with basic toiletries, a television, and a small wardrobe.

data.name: richTextBox3.Text
data.value:
Offers a higher level of comfort and luxury compared to standard rooms.
Provides additional amenities such as a mini-bar, plush bathrobes, slippers, and a higher quality of toiletries. include extra perks like complimentary breakfast, access to a fitness center or spa, and personalized concierge services.

data.name: richTextBox4.Text
data.value:
Combines living and sleeping areas into one open space, suitable for longer stays or guests who prefer more flexibility.
Offers a fully-equipped kitchenette or kitchen, allowing guests to prepare their meals and enjoy the convenience of a home-away-from-home experience.

data.name: richTextBox5.Text
data.value:
Represents the epitome of luxury accommodation, perfect for discerning travelers seeking indulgence and exclusivity.
Consists of separate living and sleeping areas, providing maximum space and privacy. Lavishly decorated with high-end furnishings, luxurious fabrics, and upscale artwork.
Offers premium amenities such as a spacious bathroom with a Jacuzzi tub or rainfall shower, a private balcony or terrace, and state-of-the-art entertainment systems. includes exclusive access to VIP lounges, personalized butler service, and other elite privileges to ensure an unforgettable stay.
